bloomie-aura/
│
├── 📁 public/
│   ├── logo.png                    ← ✅ Aapka logo (tab + website dono jagah)
│   └── 📁 images/
│       └── candle1.jpg, candle2.jpg, candle3.jpg  ← Product photos
│
├── 📁 src/
│   ├── 📁 components/
│   │   ├── Navbar.jsx              ← Top bar (logo + menu)
│   │   ├── HeroSection.jsx         ← "blooming beauty, lasting aura"
│   │   ├── ProductCard.jsx         ← Candle card with add to cart
│   │   ├── OrderForm.jsx           ← Flipkart-style form
│   │   └── Confetti.jsx            ← Success page celebration
│   │
│   ├── 📁 pages/
│   │   ├── HomePage.jsx            ← Hero + Products (sab kuch yahi)
│   │   ├── CartPage.jsx            ← Order form
│   │   └── SuccessPage.jsx         ← Thank you + confetti
│   │
│   ├── App.jsx                     ← Routing (Home, Cart, Success)
│   ├── index.js                    ← React DOM render
│   └── style.css                   ← ALL styling ek file mein
│
├── 📁 backend/                     ← Node.js API (Render pe deploy)
│   ├── server.js                   ← Express server (sab kuch yahi)
│   └── package.json                ← Backend dependencies
│
├── index.html                      ← Main HTML file
├── package.json                    ← Frontend dependencies
└── vercel.json                     ← Vercel deploy settings
